==Finnish==
===Suffix===
-stö
# forming collective noun from simple noun

::'''nimistö''' ''nomenclature'' (from '''nimi''' ''name'')

::'''ymparistö''' ''environment'' (from '''ympäri''' ''around'')

===Variation===

-stö is a front vowel version of -sto according to the rules of vowel harmony

